{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"none"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors\/OnDownActionStrategySettings","preciseIdentifier":"s:17DistributedActors28OnDownActionStrategySettingsV","text":"OnDownActionStrategySettings"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When using this mode you should take special care to implement some form of shutting down of this node (!)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors\/Cluster\/MemberStatus\/down"},{"type":"text","text":" node is effectively useless for the rest of the cluster – i.e. other"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"members MUST refuse communication with this down node."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/distributedactors\/ondownactionstrategysettings\/none"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DistributedActors\/documentation\/DistributedActors\/OnDownActionStrategySettings\/none","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Take no (automatic) action upon noticing that this member is marked as [.down]."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"none"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"OnDownActionStrategySettings","preciseIdentif